data.description: Welcome to this charming two-story home that provides a harmonious blend of function and comfort! It has a 2-car garage & RV gate with dedicated parking spaces. Discover an inviting great room paired with a bay window, tons of natural light and new soft carpet in all the right places. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet and counter space and a peninsula w/a breakfast bar. Versatile loft upstairs caters to various lifestyle needs! Main bedroom boasts a walk-in closet and a full bath w/dual sinks for added comfort. The large backyard, with its covered patio, offers a perfect spot for relaxing & entertaining.  There's ample space for a pool. NO HOA! Don't miss out!
